cz.melkamar.andruian.viewlink.model.place

Class Place

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.melkamar.andruian.viewlink.model.place.MapElement
      • cz.melkamar.andruian.viewlink.model.place.Place
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.google.maps.android.clustering.ClusterItem, java.io.Serializable

    public class Place
extends MapElement
implements java.io.Serializable, com.google.maps.android.clustering.ClusterItem
    A class representing a single concrete place from the "source" dataset. A place is linked to a location object through its IRI and keeps a reference to its parent data definition object.
